<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>GPU Insight Lab Performance and Validation Report</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --color-primary: #1a237e;
    --color-accent: #00bcd4;
    --color-bg: #f5f5f5;
    --color-card: #ffffff;
    --color-border: #e0e0e0;
    --color-text: #212121;
    --color-muted: #757575;
    --color-green: #2e7d32;
    --color-yellow: #f57f17;
    --color-red: #c62828;
    --color-info: #0277bd;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  header {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 24px 32px;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  header .subtitle {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 24px 32px;
  }
  .section {
    background: var(--color-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .section-header {
    background: #eeeeee;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .section-body { padding: 16px; }
  .score-display {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 16px;
  }
  .score-circle {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .score-circle .score-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .score-details { flex: 1; }
  .score-details p { margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .kv-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .kv-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .kv-key {
    min-width: 160px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .kv-value { color: var(--color-text); word-break: break-all; }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  thead th {
    background: #eeeeee;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: #fafafa; }
  tbody td {
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .badge-info { background: #e1f5fe; color: var(--color-info); }
  .badge-warning { background: #fff8e1; color: var(--color-yellow); }
  .badge-error, .badge-critical { background: #ffebee; color: var(--color-red); }
  .badge-healthy { background: #e8f5e9; color: var(--color-green); }
  .badge-pass { background: #e8f5e9; color: var(--color-green); }
  .badge-fail { background: #ffebee; color: var(--color-red); }
  .diag-block {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-border);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
  }
  .diag-block.sev-info { border-color: var(--color-info); }
  .diag-block.sev-warning { border-color: var(--color-yellow); }
  .diag-block.sev-error, .diag-block.sev-critical { border-color: var(--color-red); }
  .diag-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 14px; }
  .diag-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .diag-summary { margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
  .diag-evidence {
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .diag-rec {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-info);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .positive-list { list-style: none; }
  .positive-list li::before { content: "✓ "; color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 700; }
  .positive-list li { margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
  .missing-list { list-style: none; }
  .missing-list li::before { content: "– "; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .missing-list li { margin-bottom: 3px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .limitations-box {
    background: #fff3e0;
    border: 1px solid #ffb300;
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .meta-block {
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    background: #f5f5f5;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  .tool-yes { color: var(--color-green); font-weight: 600; }
  .tool-no { color: var(--color-muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>GPU Insight Lab Performance and Validation Report</h1>
  <div class="subtitle">Cross-Vendor GPU Performance, Validation and Workload Diagnostics &nbsp;·&nbsp; v{{ app_version }}</div>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <!-- Score Section -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">GPU Insight Score</div>
    <div class="score-display">
      <div class="score-circle">
        <span>{{ score|round(1) if score is not none else "N/A" }}</span>
        <span class="score-label">/ 100</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-details">
        <p><strong>Confidence:</strong> {{ (confidence * 100)|round(0)|int if confidence is not none else "N/A" }}%</p>
        {% if positive_findings %}
        <p style="margin-top:8px;"><strong>Positive Findings:</strong></p>
        <ul class="positive-list">
          {% for pf in positive_findings[:6] %}
          <li>{{ pf }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}
        {% if missing_data %}
        <p style="margin-top:8px;"><strong>Missing Data:</strong></p>
        <ul class="missing-list">
          {% for md in missing_data[:6] %}
          <li>{{ md }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- System Summary -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">System Summary</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="kv-grid">
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Hostname</span><span class="kv-value">{{ sys_info.hostname|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">OS</span><span class="kv-value">{{ sys_info.os_name|default('') }} {{ sys_info.os_release|default('') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">CPU</span><span class="kv-value">{{ sys_info.cpu_model|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Logical Cores</span><span class="kv-value">{{ sys_info.cpu_logical_cores|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">RAM Total</span><span class="kv-value">{{ "%.1f"|format(sys_info.ram_total_gb) }} GB</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Python</span><span class="kv-value">{{ sys_info.python_version|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">GPU</span><span class="kv-value">{{ nv_info.gpu_name|default('Not detected') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Driver Version</span><span class="kv-value">{{ nv_info.driver_version|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">CUDA Driver</span><span class="kv-value">{{ nv_info.cuda_driver_version|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">VRAM Total</span><span class="kv-value">{{ "%.0f"|format(nv_info.vram_total_mb) }} MB</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Temperature</span><span class="kv-value">{{ "%.0f"|format(nv_info.temperature_c) }} °C</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">PCIe Link</span><span class="kv-value">Gen{{ pcie_info.pcie_gen_current|default('?') }} x{{ pcie_info.pcie_width_current|default('?') }}</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Toolchain Status -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Toolchain Status</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Tool</th><th>Available</th><th>Version</th><th>Path</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for tool_name, status in tools.items() %}
          <tr>
            <td><strong>{{ tool_name }}</strong></td>
            <td>
              {% if status.exists %}
              <span class="tool-yes">Yes</span>
              {% else %}
              <span class="tool-no">No</span>
              {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td>{{ status.version|default('N/A') }}</td>
            <td style="font-size:11px;color:#999">{{ status.path|default('') }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Benchmark Results -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Benchmark Results</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      {% if results %}
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Test</th>
            <th>Mean (ms)</th>
            <th>Median (ms)</th>
            <th>Std Dev</th>
            <th>BW (GB/s)</th>
            <th>Speedup</th>
            <th>Correct</th>
            <th>Notes</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for r in results %}
          <tr>
            <td><strong>{{ r.test_name|default('') }}</strong></td>
            <td>{{ "%.3f"|format(r.mean) if r.mean is not none else 'N/A' }}</td>
            <td>{{ "%.3f"|format(r.median) if r.median is not none else 'N/A' }}</td>
            <td>{{ "%.3f"|format(r.standard_deviation) if r.standard_deviation is not none else 'N/A' }}</td>
            <td>{{ "%.2f"|format(r.bandwidth_gbps) if r.bandwidth_gbps is not none else 'N/A' }}</td>
            <td>{{ "%.1f"|format(r.speedup) if r.speedup is not none else 'N/A' }}</td>
            <td>
              {% if r.correctness_pass == true %}
              <span class="badge badge-pass">Pass</span>
              {% elif r.correctness_pass == false %}
              <span class="badge badge-fail">Fail</span>
              {% else %}
              <span style="color:#999">N/A</span>
              {% endif %}
            </td>
            <td style="font-size:12px;color:#666">{{ r.notes|default('') }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
      {% else %}
      <p style="color:#999">No benchmark results available.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Diagnosis -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Diagnosis Results</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      {% if diag_results %}
      {% for d in diag_results %}
      <div class="diag-block sev-{{ d.severity|lower }}">
        <div class="diag-title">
          <span class="badge badge-{{ d.severity|lower }}">{{ d.severity }}</span>
          &nbsp;{{ d.title|default('') }}
        </div>
        <div class="diag-meta">
          Category: <strong>{{ d.category|default('') }}</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
          Confidence: <strong>{{ (d.confidence * 100)|round(0)|int if d.confidence is not none else 'N/A' }}%</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="diag-summary">{{ d.summary|default('') }}</div>
        {% if d.evidence %}
        <div class="diag-evidence">{{ d.evidence }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if d.recommendation %}
        <div class="diag-rec">Recommendation: {{ d.recommendation }}</div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if d.verification_step %}
        <div class="diag-rec" style="margin-top:4px">Verification: {{ d.verification_step }}</div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
      <p style="color:#999">No diagnosis results available.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Recommendations Summary -->
  {% if recommendations %}
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Top Recommendations</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul style="padding-left:20px">
        {% for rec in recommendations %}
        <li style="margin-bottom:8px;font-size:13px">{{ rec }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Raw Metadata -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Session Metadata</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="kv-grid">
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Session Name</span><span class="kv-value">{{ session_name|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Session ID</span><span class="kv-value">{{ session_id|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Started At</span><span class="kv-value">{{ started_at|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Completed At</span><span class="kv-value">{{ completed_at|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Status</span><span class="kv-value">{{ status|default('N/A') }}</span></div>
        <div class="kv-item"><span class="kv-key">Report Generated</span><span class="kv-value">{{ generated_at }}</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Interview Demo Summary -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Interview Demo Summary — Implemented vs. Roadmap Features</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <p style="margin-bottom:12px;font-size:13px"><strong>GPU Insight Lab v{{ app_version }}</strong> — Feature Coverage</p>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px">
        <div>
          <p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;color:#2e7d32">Implemented Features</p>
          <ul style="padding-left:16px;font-size:13px">
            <li>System Inspector (CPU/GPU/PCIe/CUDA telemetry)</li>
            <li>Memory Benchmark (H2D/D2H/D2D via native CUDA binary)</li>
            <li>Kernel Lab (vector_add, reduction, transpose, gemm_naive, gemm_tiled, stream_pipeline)</li>
            <li>Evidence-based Diagnosis Engine (9 rules)</li>
            <li>GPU Insight Score (0-100 composite, 6 categories)</li>
            <li>Multi-format Reports (JSON, CSV, Markdown, HTML, Excel)</li>
            <li>SQLite Session History with delta comparison</li>
            <li>PySide6 GUI (QMainWindow + QThread workers)</li>
            <li>CLI Automation (10 commands, --json flag)</li>
            <li>CUDA to HIP Portability Demo (vector_add_hip.cpp)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;color:#c62828">Roadmap / NOT YET IMPLEMENTED</p>
          <ul style="padding-left:16px;font-size:13px;color:#666">
            <li>ROADMAP: softmax, layer_norm, GELU, Flash Attention</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: INT8 quantization kernel</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: PyTorch extension / TensorRT plugin</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: cuFFT / cuBLAS full benchmark suite</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: Streamlit dashboard</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: Parquet storage backend</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: Multi-machine import / batch execution</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: Company report templates</li>
            <li>ROADMAP: Pass/fail policy configuration</li>
            <li>NOT_VALIDATED: AMD HIP real GPU benchmarks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Missing Data -->
  {% if missing_data %}
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Missing Data</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <ul style="padding-left:20px;font-size:13px">
        {% for item in missing_data %}
        <li>{{ item }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- Limitations -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">Limitations and Disclaimers</div>
    <div class="section-body">
      <div class="limitations-box">
        <p style="margin-bottom:8px">
          GPU Insight Lab provides evidence-based diagnostics using measurable performance metrics.
          It is <strong>not a replacement</strong> for Nsight Systems or Nsight Compute for deep kernel profiling.
        </p>
        <ul style="padding-left:20px;margin-bottom:8px">
          <li>Low GPU utilization does <strong>not</strong> automatically mean the GPU is the bottleneck.</li>
          <li>Low occupancy does <strong>not</strong> automatically indicate poor performance.</li>
          <li>GEMM performance is reported without comparison to cuBLAS (which would always win).</li>
          <li>AMD/ROCm support is <strong>NOT_VALIDATED</strong> in v{{ app_version }}.</li>
          <li>All diagnosis results include evidence strings; no findings are made without data.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size:12px;color:#666">
          NVIDIA, CUDA, Nsight, AMD, ROCm, HIP, and other referenced names are trademarks of their respective owners.
          GPU Insight Lab is an independent engineering project not affiliated with or endorsed by NVIDIA or AMD.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- /container -->

<footer>
  Generated by <strong>GPU Insight Lab v{{ app_version }}</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  Cross-Vendor GPU Performance, Validation and Workload Diagnostics &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  {{ generated_at }}
</footer>

</body>
</html>
